## Develop Environment
* Visual Studio Community 2015 Update 3
* Windows Driver Kit Version 7.1.0

## Platform
* Windows 7 x64

## Mechanism
* Windows Device Driver
* SSDT(System Service Descriptor Table) Hooking
* Kernel-User Communication : Global event object, DeviceIoControl    
